<br>
As such, its combat skills should be greater.  That's not currently true with respect to the minstrel.<br>
<br>
I would like to see Evade 2.  I would also like to see a slight increase in skill points - nothing drastic mind you - say to 1.7/1.8 per level - so that we could bump up our Parry.<br>
<br>
Other issues:<br>
<br>
1.  Pulses missed - speed song and damage add - must be fixed.<br>
<br>
2.  Range of damage add - 700 far to short.  1500 would be nice.<br>
<br>
3.  DD shout timer - currently 20 seconds, should be 15 secs.<br>
<br>
4.  Resist songs - would love for a solo skald to be able to sing 3 or even 2 resists in one song.<br>
<br>
5.  Class RA - needs to be fixed.  I would like to see some kind of combined damage add/parry-shield blocking - evade enhancement group RA (makes sure it stacks on whatever Savages are doing). <br>
<br>
6.  New song - not sure what this should be, but the thread you started on this contains some very nice ideas.<br>
<br>
7.  Speed song - should not drop unless the skald singing it is either attacked or is attacking.<br>
<br>
That's it. <br>
