Halving the duration, but doubling the damage...and having it cost 10 RA Points akin to BoF for clerics.  I think this is appropriate especially b/c it highly depends on each person having high resists....and while most people I RvR with do, not everyone does.<br>
<br>
NOTE:  I would still rather see this happen as a shout and not an RA.  I think on a 10 minute timer and having a lvl 50 BS requirement for the 100% reflect, its not overpowered.  Especially not after the ablative buff that minstels just got.<br>
